[15.959, "o", "I need to forge a new tool. Here's the forged tool:\r\n\r\n**TODO Scanner Tool (v1.0)**  \r\n- Scans files for `TODO`, `FIXME`, `HACK` comments  \r\n- Categorizes by priority:  \r\n  - P0: `TODO(P0)` / `FIXME(P0)` / `HACK(P0)`  \r\n  - P1: `TODO(P1)` / `FIXME(P1)` / `HACK(P1)`  \r\n  - P2: Default priority if no tag is present  \r\n- Outputs structured results with file/line/context  \r\n\r\n**Scan Results (example):**  \r\n```yaml\r\npriority: P0\r\n- file: packages/kbot/src/utils.js\r\n  line: 42\r\n  context: \"TODO(P0): Optimize memory usage for large datasets\"\r\n\r\npriority: P2\r\n- file: packages/kbot/src/api.js\r\n  line: 15\r\n  context: \"FIXME: Handle edge case where token is null\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nWould you like me to execute this scan now?\r\n"]
